Name: primark
Caption: Come with jo_the_futurist to our #PrimarkCares event 💙 .Primark Cares has nine commitments across three key areas – product planet and people. These commitments range from making all our clothes from recycled or more sustainably sourced materials by 2030 halving carbon emissions across our supply chain over the next seven years and pursuing a living wage for workers in our supply chain. All of the decor for the event was repurposed from other events and included QR codes and information about the programme. The food was sourced locally to minimise the event’s impact and everyone was invited to take home leftovers to minimise food waste. We welcomed influencers and the press to talk about the programme and open up an important conversation about the impact of fashion.
